Individual




Robert E. Switz



Mr. Robert E. Switz is Chairman at Micron Technology, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Marvell Technology Group Ltd., Gigamon, Inc., GT Advanced Technologies, Inc., GTAT Corp. and The Communications & Information Technology Association. Mr. Switz was previously employed as an Independent Director by Cricket Wireless LLC, an Independent Director by Cyan, Inc., a Lead Independent Director by Broadcom Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by ADC Ventures, Inc., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by ADC Telecommunications, Inc., CFO, VP, Director-Ventures & Systems Business by Burr Brown Corp., a Principal by SliceCo, Inc., a Principal by Olin Mathieson Chemical Corp., and President & Chief Executive Officer by Fiber Optic Network Solutions Corp. He also served on the board at Pulse Electronics Corp., Hickory Tech Corporation and Telecommunications Industry Association. He received his undergraduate degree from Quinnipiac University and an MBA from the University of Bridgeport.



